vernac_cmds: Require Import ZArith NArith Nnat Ndec Ndigits.
Variable gc : BDDconfig -> list ad -> BDDconfig.
Hypothesis l_used' : used_node' cfg ul l.
Hypothesis r_used' : used_node' cfg ul r.
Hypothesis l_neq_r : Neqb l r = false.
Hypothesis xl_lt_x : forall (xl : BDDvar) (ll rl : ad), MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg cfg) l = Some (xl, (ll, rl)) -> BDDcompare xl x = Datatypes.Lt.
Hypothesis xr_lt_x : forall (xr : BDDvar) (lr rr : ad), MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg cfg) r = Some (xr, (lr, rr)) -> BDDcompare xr x = Datatypes.Lt.
Hypothesis no_dup : forall (x' : BDDvar) (l' r' a : ad), MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg cfg) a = Some (x', (l', r')) -> (x, (l, r)) <> (x', (l', r')).
Lemma no_dup_new : forall (x' : BDDvar) (l' r' a : ad), MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) a = Some (x', (l', r')) -> (x, (l, r)) <> (x', (l', r')).
Lemma new_cfg_nodes_preserved : used_nodes_preserved cfg new_cfg ul.
Lemma new_xl_lt_x : forall (xl : BDDvar) (ll rl : ad), MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) l = Some (xl, (ll, rl)) -> BDDcompare xl x = Datatypes.Lt.
elim y1; intros y2 y3 y4.
Lemma new_xr_lt_x : forall (xr : BDDvar) (lr rr : ad), MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) r = Some (xr, (lr, rr)) -> BDDcompare xr x = Datatypes.Lt.
elim y1; intros y2 y3 y4.

Definition BDDalloc : BDDconfig * ad := match new_cfg with | (bs, (share, (fl, (cnt, (negm, orm))))) => match fl with | a :: fl' => (MapPut _ bs a (x, (l, r)), (MapPut3 _ share l r x a, (fl', (cnt, (negm, orm)))), a) | nil => (MapPut _ bs cnt (x, (l, r)), (MapPut3 _ share l r x cnt, (fl, (ad_S cnt, (negm, orm)))), cnt) end end.
Lemma BDDalloc_lemma_1 : forall a : ad, MapGet _ (fst (fst BDDalloc)) a = (if Neqb a (snd BDDalloc) then Some (x, (l, r)) else MapGet _ (fst new_cfg) a).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) (cnt_of_cfg new_cfg) (x, (l, r)) a).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) x0 (x, (l, r)) a).
Lemma BDDalloc_lemma_2 : In (snd BDDalloc) (fl_of_cfg new_cfg) \/ cnt_of_cfg new_cfg = snd BDDalloc.
Lemma BDDalloc_lemma_3 : MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) (snd BDDalloc) = None.
Lemma BDDalloc_lemma_4 : fst (fst BDDalloc) = MapPut _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) (snd BDDalloc) (x, (l, r)).
Lemma BDDalloc_lemma_5 : fst (snd (fst BDDalloc)) = MapPut3 _ (share_of_cfg new_cfg) l r x (snd BDDalloc).
Lemma BDDalloc_zero : MapGet _ (fst (fst BDDalloc)) BDDzero = None.
Lemma BDDalloc_one : MapGet _ (fst (fst BDDalloc)) BDDone = None.
cut (MapGet (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (fst (fst BDDalloc)) (snd BDDalloc) = Some (x, (l, r))).
apply BDDbounded_2 with (x := x) (l := l) (r := r).
cut (BDDcompare (ad_S xl) x = Datatypes.Lt \/ ad_S xl = x).
cut (BDDcompare (ad_S xr) x = Datatypes.Lt \/ ad_S xr = x).
elim x0; clear x0; intros x1 y0.
elim y0; clear y0; intros l1 r1.
cut (MapGet (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (fst (fst BDDalloc)) a = Some (x1, (l1, r1))).
Lemma BDDsharing_OK_1 : forall a : ad, MapGet _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) a = None -> BDDsharing_OK (MapPut _ (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) a (x, (l, r))) (MapPut3 _ (share_of_cfg new_cfg) l r x a).
rewrite (MapPut3_semantics ad (share_of_cfg new_cfg) l r x l0 r0 x0 a).
elim (sumbool_of_bool (Neqb l l0 && (Neqb r r0 && Neqb x x0))).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) a (x, (l, r)) a) .
cut (Neqb l l0 = true /\ Neqb r r0 = true /\ Neqb x x0 = true).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) a (x, (l, r)) a0).
rewrite (proj1 (proj1 (proj2 new_cfg_OK) x0 l0 r0 a) H0) in H.
exact (proj1 (proj1 (proj2 new_cfg_OK) x0 l0 r0 a0) H0).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) a (x, (l, r)) a0).
rewrite (MapPut3_semantics ad (share_of_cfg new_cfg) l r x l r x a).
rewrite (MapPut3_semantics ad (share_of_cfg new_cfg) l r x l0 r0 x0 a).
cut (Neqb l l0 && (Neqb r r0 && Neqb x x0) = false).
exact (proj2 (proj1 (proj2 new_cfg_OK) x0 l0 r0 a0) H0).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) (cnt_of_cfg new_cfg) (x, (l, r)) a).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) x0 (x, (l, r)) a).
Lemma BDDalloc_keeps_free_list_OK : BDDfree_list_OK (fst (fst BDDalloc)) (fst (snd (snd (fst BDDalloc)))) (fst (snd (snd (snd (fst BDDalloc))))).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) (cnt_of_cfg new_cfg) (x, (l, r)) node).
rewrite (MapPut_semantics (BDDvar * (ad * ad)) (bs_of_cfg new_cfg) x0 (x, (l, r)) node).
Lemma BDDalloc_orm_same : orm_of_cfg (fst BDDalloc) = orm_of_cfg new_cfg.
Lemma BDDalloc_negm_same : negm_of_cfg (fst BDDalloc) = negm_of_cfg new_cfg.
Lemma BDDalloc_um_same : um_of_cfg (fst BDDalloc) = um_of_cfg new_cfg.
Lemma BDDalloc_preserves_used_nodes : used_nodes_preserved cfg (fst BDDalloc) ul.
Lemma BDDallocGet : MapGet _ (fst (fst BDDalloc)) (snd BDDalloc) = Some (x, (l, r)).
